channel.title: Login isnt working?
channel.description: Every time i login with the for-sure correct account,which i use for forums,it wont work! It always says 'please wait 1 minute and try again'. When that doesnt happen,it says the server wont respond.

item.title: Login isnt working?
item.dc:creator: @_Rich Rich
item.description:
@_Rich wrote:

You don’t have to login with your forum username or password, you can login with anything you want. Make sure you’re connecting to a valid IP (by looking at servers on the status page).

Also, if you ever get a return message ‘error connecting to server’, it means the server is offline.
